    Subclasses of Island in islands 
    Modifier and Type Class Description
    class  Fodina
    Fodina is a mining island
    Has expensive food and tools, but cheap luxury and materials
    class  Officina
    Officina is a manufactory
    Has cheap artifacts and tools, and materials are expensive
    class  Pratum
    Pratium is the starting island
    Has cheap food and materials, but luxuries and artifacts are more valuable
    class  Tempestas
    Tempestas is a stormy island.
    Has cheap food, and above retail price for tools, artifacts, and luxury goods.
    class  Terminus
    Terminus is an isolated pirate haven.
    Food, tools, and materials are expensive.
